hopobject.body: I live in London plexus 96 shakes The decision comes as New York Attorney General Eric Schneiderman conducts an investigation into the scope and impact of the early dissemination of the report. Schneiderman said Monday that the "two second advantage is more than enough time for [high speed] traders to take unfair advantage of their early access to this information as they execute enormous volumes of trades in the blink of an eye."
